# Beauty pass
Format 1920 1080 1.0
PixelFilter "mitchell" 2.5 2.5
PixelSamples 6 6
Option "limits" "bucketsize" [ 32 32 ]
Display "beauty.tif" "file" "rgb"
Display "+beauty" "framebuffer" "rgb"
Projection "perspective" "fov" [ 30.0 ]
Translate 0 -1.5 15
Rotate -110 1 0 0
DepthOfField 4.0 1.0 14
WorldBegin
  Surface "matteocclusion"
          "string ptCloudName" [ "occlusion.ptc" ]
          "float baking" [ 0 ]
  ReadArchive "world.rib"
WorldEnd
